{"tid":2357642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(己 澄 清）龍 門 冰 室 老 闆 一 句 KO 渣 狗 分 化 撚","createTime":"2021-01-07T14:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T15:09:27.000Z","uid":361751,"like":26,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2df086db51059ddaf95155ce959d281f1961c0ff","tid":2357642,"uid":361751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T14:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/70W2NuV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F70W2NuV.png&h=70aab50b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇到傳真社<br />\n就住龍門冰室同富臨「有關係」嘅報道<br />\n我想收返起 平日掛喺臉上嘅笑臉<br />\n簡單回應幾句<br />\n<br />\n我過往已經喺公開訪問講過好多次<br />\n我同富臨嘅關係 喺運動後經已了斷咗<br />\n詳情大家可以上網搜尋返<br />\n維基百科大把<br />\n<br />\n而今次傳真社「如獲至寶」搵到嘅呢一間<br />\n「鼎盛宏英餐飲有限公司」<br />\n其實只係單單擁有<br />\n屯門海麗花園嘅舊加盟店<br />\n但最搞笑嘅係 記者你知唔知<br />\n呢一間舖頭喺2019年11月已經無再營業<br />\n咁我到今時今刻仲點同富臨<br />\n有啲乜嘢生意來往呢？<br />\n懇請記者做報道時需要謹慎啲⋯<br />\n<br />\n用上煽動性嘅標題 去嘩眾取寵<br />\n做一張好複雜嘅關係圖<br />\n然後為我扣上「莫須有」嘅罪名<br />\n無錯 你哋的確成功博取到公眾嘅眼球<br />\n<br />\n但請唔好忘記<br />\n傳媒嘅字句其實猶如一把利刃<br />\n如果無好好咁去運用<br />\n以及Fact Check手上嘅素材資料 胡亂報道<br />\n最終只會淪為「中共」嘅武器<br />\n<br />\n#我都整咗張八卦圖"},{"pid":"e7a51a2ca9e60c04f8dcba23a930e5297b949fca","tid":2357642,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T14:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d025641975f299c695ca94d7ce29dcd63fda1201","tid":2357642,"uid":19528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T14:22:41.000Z","msg":"頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0c8bbae3520ab169064b9e1c4231db351bb331","tid":2357642,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"